# Evaluator Rubric — qcomm-knowledge-query vs spec-rag baseline

Issue protocol: 2026-05-17_volte-call-drop
Date: fill on eval run
Evaluator: fill on eval run

---

## Scoring Guide

All criteria are binary (pass=1, fail=0) unless marked with weight.
Normalize raw score to /10 scale per test as documented in each UT file.

### Output Quality Dimensions (apply to all tests)

| ID | Dimension | Description | Weight |
|----|-----------|-------------|--------|
| D1 | Format Usability | Output directly usable without manual extraction | 2 |
| D2 | RAT Specificity | Results scoped to correct RAT (no cross-RAT leakage) | 2 |
| D3 | Schema Completeness | All required fields present in output | 3 |
| D4 | Reference Quality | TS/doc references with section numbers | 2 |
| D5 | Qualcomm Specificity | Vendor-specific content included where applicable | 1 |

---

