- Average delta ≥ +4: SKILL STRONGLY ADDS VALUE
- Average delta +2 to +3: SKILL MODERATELY ADDS VALUE
- Average delta < +2: SKILL NEEDS REWORK

---

## Regression Policy

Run this full rubric after every change to SKILL.md.
Any test where "With Skill" score drops by ≥ 2 points vs previous run = regression, block merge.

## V1 Known Weakness Tracking

| Weakness | UT | Expected V1 Score | Action if confirmed |
|----------|-----|-------------------|---------------------|
| W2: cross_layer single module | UT-03 | 5/10 (FAIL) | Prioritize V2 fix |
| W5: no doc_type filter | UT-01, UT-04 | partial degradation | V2 fix |
| W8: hardcoded corpus | UT-06 | may degrade if vendor docs absent | V2 configurable corpus |
